HWPX Format Specification
This software implements document parsing and generation based on the
publicly available HWPX (HWP Open XML) specification published by Hancom Inc.

Reference: https://www.hancom.com/support/downloadCenter/hwpOwpml
Standard: KS X 6101 (Korean Industrial Standard for HWP Open XML)

The HWPX format specification is published by Hancom Inc. and is available
for implementation without restriction. This software does not use, copy,
or derive from any Hancom proprietary source code.

